org.codefx.libfx.nesting.Nesting

  • Packages that use Nesting 
    Package Description
    org.codefx.libfx.nesting
    This package provides functionality around nesting hierarchies - a term which is explained in all detail in the comment on Nesting.
    org.codefx.libfx.nesting.listener
    Contains nested listeners and builders for them.
    org.codefx.libfx.nesting.property
    Contains the definition for NestedProperty as well as its implementations (a generic NestedObjectProperty and its primitive type wrapping counterparts) and builders for them.
